@Node DADS9 "Dad's Army > The Loneliness Of The Long Distance Walker [#9]"

 @{b}The Loneliness Of The Long Distance Walker [#9]@{ub} (1969)
 
 Walker is called up which is bad news for the platoon because of his
 deftness in acquiring essential supplies like cigarettes, booze and fudge
 for Godfrey's sister. Mainwaring decides that Walker is too important to
 the platoon to let him go, so he fights the War Office on his behalf.
 
 His valiant attempts fail and Walker joins the army. But within days he's
 discharged, much to the relief of the platoon, when it's discovered he's
